name: Chanel No. 5 Eau de Parfum - Classic Floral Fragrance
description: Chanel No. 5 Eau de Parfum is a timeless fragrance that epitomizes classic elegance. Launched in 1921, this iconic scent is known for its sophisticated blend of floral and musky notes. With a captivating top note of ylang-ylang and neroli, a heart of jasmine and rose, and a warm base of sandalwood and vanilla, Chanel No. 5 offers a luxurious and enduring fragrance experience. Ideal for both daytime and evening wear, this perfume is perfect for women who appreciate a touch of sophistication and grace in their fragrance collection.
